title: Yavli
shortDescription: Serve non-intrusive ads to ad blocking visitors.
longDescription:
**Monetize visitors accessing your website with ad blockers.**

* Install and start earning
* Ads fill 'whitespace' created by ad blockers
* Easy revenue win
* Monthly payments
* Non-intrusive native ads
* No upfront fees or ongoing maintenance

**FAQs**

*What % of my website visitors use ad blockers?*   
Most websites we work with are in the 10-15% range.   

*Will this slow down my page load times?*   
Nope. Yavli ads load asynchronously.

*Do I need to position the ads myself?*   
No. We will do this for you.

*Can I have a say in where ads appear on my website?*   
If you have a specific preference please email publishers@yavli.com.

*What type of ad content does Yavli display?*   
Native ad thumbnails that link to advertorials and sponsored videos.

*How do I know Yavli won't inject ads for non-ad blocker users?*   
If we misbehave Cloudflare would terminate our app.

*How do I get paid?*   
Please submit your bank payment details to publishers@yavli.com.

*When do I get paid?*   
Monthly. Net 45.
instructions: To install Yavli you will need a unique Website ID and API key. Please email your company name and website URL to publishers@yavli.com if you do not already have this.
author: Yavli Limited
